=CIPs=

People willing to submit CIPs should visit
https://burstwiki.org/wiki/CIP and follow the predefined
workflow. After discussion on the Burst Discord Server, please open a
PR. After copy-editing and acceptance, it will be published here.

Having a CIP listed here doesn't guarantee it is an accepted standard
until its status becomes Final or Active.

